column3: “Mood was brighter, pain was managed, everything was fun, and music was amazing. Euphoric and talkative.”
“A very nice strain. At first a headhigh, whitch turns slowly into a smooth stoned. Like it.”

“The Strain Highlights are wrong on this one.
 https://www.dinafem.org/en/critical-cheese/

Critical Cheese cannabis seeds by Dinafem Seeds is a feminized, Indica-dominant cannabis strain that originates from the cross of a Cheese and a Critical +. It is the merger of two of our strains renowned for their amazing flavor and aroma.

Critical Cheese is part of the foundations of our building and even cannabis connoisseu...”

“As someone who has a hard time with more stimulating strains this was the perfect amount without causing me anxiety. I really like cheese for the light sativa effects, while retaining the warmth of an indica.”

“This is really a great strain if you feel like you wanna be active, out walking or just partying. It smells very sweet, like some candy, and it got a mild taste, which is bushy and just, tastes like traditional weed. 
I'm at an 9/10 now from this, so yeah :D”

“Mood was brighter, pain was managed, everything was fun, and music was amazing. Euphoric and talkative. 
Very nice afternoon to evening strain. Went back and got another eighth.”
“First high is high, then chill.”
“Delightful high, I felt relaxed yet energized. I gave it three stars because I don't like weed that makes me hungry. Unfortunately, this one does.”
“This cheese had me talking my ass off.  Very fun and deep highs with this strain for me”
“wakey wakey eggs and bakey”
“A great hybrid, best for daytime but also good for a relaxing evening smoke. Has earthy and fruity notes, and is VERY pungent. Both novice and experienced smokers will enjoy this one.”
“Very nice smell, very relaxing makes you cough a lot but damn it makes talking easier also”
“This was amazing.  fav strain I was like HOLY SHIT.”
“Good. Great, hyper, creative high for about 2 hours. Then you become a couch potato.”

“This batch of Critical Cheese tested in at over 30% THC! I could feel that desired whirling feeling in my head upon the first hit. I do not usually care for Cheese strains, but this has won me over with its hard-hitting fast-acting giggly and energizing effects.”
“Specific taste, something like mint with little bit of honey.”
“Good smell but not very intense, amazing citric flavour with a very potent and energetic high”

“Está dentro de las mejores marihuanas que he provado,
ya sea,por su efecto armonioso,feliz ,motivante y sociable. 
ideal para compartir y reir con amigos”
“im not a real fan of critical, but this one is real nice. strong sativa and clean high”

“Aroma: Citrus/Cheesey
Flavor: Sweet/Earthy
Smoke is mild
5 minute onset with increasing effect
Energetic high with a bit of scatter brain.
good for depression”

“Really nice looking . Smell got me uplifted right away . Usually I need more indica ish hybrids to better manage my mood since sativa tend to make me more anxious , but this one got me feeling giddy. Exactly what I needed after a full week of being stuck in a circle of unproductive thoughts .”

“Bought this cheap so thought it was going to be just the mellow type. Was surprised when I first smoked it and the affect it had on me and some pals. Two joints worth and it hits you hard. However, just having the right amounts presses the buttons as you can be energetic of small doses. Very smooth on the throat too.”
“Good vibes smoked it in hash form”
“great stoney body feeling with a euphoric head buzz. drys eyes and mouth comes with it.”
“great strain to get things done around the house or for a night out on the town with friends.”
“meds to the max great for nerves!calmed me down and helped me get a full night sleep!”
“nice”
“The cheese is sure to please. Mellow relaxing feeling but still gives energy to do anything interesting”

“Good bud from the smoking perspective.
As far as growing this strain it tends to be weak with fox-tailing in the last couple of weeks of flower.

Look at greenhouse cheese or even better DR Krippling IncredibleBulk.
You won't regret it.”
“It isn't a powerful kick, but there is one that mellows off into a body high.”

“Has a kush look and cheese taste floaty mellow high.
Made nice rosin solventless extract fro strain .”
“This strains effects produce a clear-headed and focus mind. Visuals are sharper and clearer. Experiencing a light feel on the effect of the body. Overall, a great strain for daytime use.”
“Very potent Dank ...light smoke, with Pungent, Sharp cheese smell and taste. Feeling very euphoric and focused”
“Pretty nice flavor, and the hught is betther than the ususal once.”
“Excellent flavor with frosty trichomes. Large yield for a 60 plant. Clones easy. Happy uplifting high. Edibles provide some hallucinations, and tingle spine.”

“I love cheese. this strain isn't the best iv ever had but it is very nice. relaxing and uplifting. does not give me the foggy mind like most cheese strains. lowers my pain slightly just enough to process at work. tho this crop I have is too dry . but still good. and no seeds found”
“Mostly cerebral. Makes me social.”

“I’m a very seasoned (3-5 bowl/day) smoker with access to a very nice variety of strains and I alternative strains as well to avoid tolerance. In fact, I’ve been noticing diminishing returns lately and have even considered a t-break. I normally smoke early (after coffee) but today waited until I finished running some errands. I got home loaded a bowl of Critical Cheese and was immediately, and I mean IMMEDIATELY hit w...”
“This was amazing.  fav strain I was like HOLY SHIT.”

“This is a great hybrid for being able to function while have the feelings of euphoria. Definite anxiety and stress reliever; makes you feel lighter (less tense muscles, less pressure on you as a whole). I gave it a four because of the dry eyes and mouth, accompanied by its eternal name sake: CHEESE! Any how, overall, I am a fan of using this strain myself, even in daytime. Night would also be very relaxing - just not...”
“Nice long high and amazing flavour. Nice smoke.”

“Grew this strain just for personal use and really enjoyed it, it’s a very intense head high if grown right but loved the high it’s a racy kinda high like you’re on some kinda upper drug I’d guess all in all very nice.”
“Specific taste, something like mint with little bit of honey.”

“Muy buena cepa, una combinación de muy rico sabor y un muy buen pegue. El sabor tiene un inconfundible dejo de Cheese, pero no necesariamente super marcado. El pegue es muy bueno, bien de Sativa, personalmente mis favoritas.
Si bien no llego a entrar en la categoría de las mejores que fumé" tampoco se quedó tan lejos
